title: REMINDER: Apply for Fall 2022 Graduation
description:
Students completing their graduation requirements by the end of Fall 2022/January 2023 semester must Apply for Graduation via Albert.*
Though related, your eligibility for attending All-University Commencement and school ceremonies are separate unique processes and more information can be found here…

description: Beginning today students who are Initially registering for fall 2022 classes will incur a late registration fee.

title: Fall 2022 100% Refund Deadline
description: Tuition and fees for individual classes dropped on or before this date will be refunded 100% for students who remain enrolled in at least one class. For term and/or total withdrawal refund information, refer to the Refund Schedule for Complete Withdrawal on the Bursar’s website.

title: Fall 2022 Withdrawal Period Begins
description:
Classes dropped on or after this date result in a “W” grade on the student transcript. To withdraw from a class, students may Request a Class Withdrawal in Albert.
Students can no longer be enrolled into a class from a waitlist and waitlists are purged.
